        <p> We dipped a coral island several times and met many small and large fish as well as 3 turtles and some giant mussels. Since the visibility was only 3 to 5 meters, Steffi did not have as much fun on the surface. She didn't get much to see. I think the biggest thing she got to see several times was her diving hare, me! </p>
		<p> On the way back to Cairns, we both were somehow disappointed with the day trip. I therefore decided that this short trip to China should not be remembered for our time at the Great Barrier Reef. Immediately when we arrived in Cairns we were looking for a tourist shop of the information about Franklands Islands. After a short consideration we booked another day trip to the reef for tomorrow. This time in the knowledge that only 100 people are approved on this island. Hopefully the ship is not full. </p>
